ygData.subject: One last note
ygData.msgSnippet: If you can teleport, I would appreciate some help over in Greater Fay. The reason I asked about the install thing is because I lag really bad in some places
ygData.messageBody:
If you can teleport, I would appreciate some help
over in Greater Fay. The reason I asked about the
install thing is because I lag really bad in some places
(like the Butcherblok Docks) and I just sit there
loading. I can never move nor camp. Eventually I am forced
to manually shut down. One time, I was lagging at
the docks and was killed by an aqua goblin. If I had
tried to get my stuff, I would have froze again. It
wasn't a big deal (thanks to my "monk"iness), but a good
friend helped me out and looted for me (thanks
Minamas!)<br><br>In short, I am needing to learn some moves I am
overdue on. If anyone can teleport me to Freeport I would
be very gratefull.
